实现LogOutputManager增强并添加RotationManagerFactory
-重构LogOutputManager，提高可读性和代码风格的一致性。 -增加了一个新的RotationManagerFactory与一个简单的旋转管理器实现。 -增强MultiOutputConfigSerializer，以便在保存/加载操作期间更好地处理文件。 -在轮换管理器中引入异步轮换功能和基本统计跟踪。 确保正确的错误处理和记录贯穿于新的轮换管理功能。

Add Snappy compression library and integrate into main application
- Introduced Snappy compression library by adding snappy.h and snappy-stubs-public.h headers. - Created binary files for both debug and release versions of Snappy. - Updated project configuration to include Snappy library paths and dependencies. - Implemented a test function for Snappy compression and decompression in main.cpp, demonstrating its usage with a sample string. - Added several new background images to the resources. - Updated README with contact information and third-party library dependencies. - Minor adjustments to existing files for better organization and clarity.
